TITLE: Comparing Old and New GraphQL APIs for Collections
DESCRIPTION: Example showing the simplified naming for collection queries, where 'getCollection' and 'getCollections' become 'collection' and 'collections' respectively.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tinacms/tinacms/blob/main/packages/@tinacms/graphql/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-20_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
# old
{
  getCollection(collection: "post") {...}
}
{
  getCollections {...}
}

# new
{
  collection(collection: "post") {...}
}
{
  collections {...}
}
```

