TITLE: Database Migration: Custom Git Provider
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet illustrates how to implement a custom Git provider by implementing the `GitProvider` interface. It shows the basic structure of a custom `GitProvider` with `onPut` and `onDelete` methods.
